19 MD: Baltimore looks to join 'gigabit cities,' including Westminster, in boosting broadband Internet capacity 
Baltimore Sun: When Google announced plans in 2010 to build an ultra-fast network somewhere in the United States, Baltimore leaders pledged to expand the city's Internet bandwidth with or without the Internet giant.
